window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A new problem arises…</b></p> <p>Now that Anthony’s existence has become known, numerous people of great importance are looking at Academy Island with interest - and some with malice.</p> <p>Among those are the seductive and secretive Selene Dracul - daughter of the Vampire Lord, Vlad Dracul - and Marianne Tepes, the young daughter of Elizabeth Tepes, another Vampire Lord but one who sues for peace between demons and humans.</p> <p>While Selene becomes a student at Anthony’s college, Marianne has gone missing. Lucretia Incanscino makes a request of Anthony. Find Marianne and escort her to Academy Island at all costs.</p> <p>Warning: contains mature content.</p>"; 
